description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Herpesvirus saimiri (type 1 / strain mv-5-4-psl); Herpesvirus saimiri 1; Herpesvirus tamarinus; Marmoset herpesvirus; Saimiriine herpesvirus 1; Squirrel monkey alphaherpesvirus type 1; Squirrel monkey herpesvirus 1; herpesvirus M).
